---
import { getSlugs } from "../data/blogs";
import { reads, books, videos } from "../data/bookmarks";
import type { MdOrMdxFile } from "../data/blogs";

const posts = await getSlugs(
  (await Astro.glob("./blog/*.md*")) as MdOrMdxFile[]
);
const notes = await getSlugs(
  (await Astro.glob("./notes/*.md*")) as MdOrMdxFile[]
);
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>For LLMs - EmNudge</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <pre>{`# EmNudge - Site Content for LLMs

This page provides structured content about emnudge.dev for language models and AI systems.

## Site Overview

EmNudge is a software developer who writes technical articles and creates YouTube videos about programming. The site focuses on JavaScript, web development, Unicode, WebAssembly, and programming concepts.

## Contact & Links

- Website: https://emnudge.dev
- GitHub: https://github.com/EmNudge
- YouTube: https://youtube.com/EmNudge
- Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/emnudge.dev

## RSS Feeds

- Blog: https://emnudge.dev/blog.xml
- Reads: https://emnudge.dev/reads.xml
- Videos: https://emnudge.dev/videos.xml
- Books: https://emnudge.dev/books.xml

## Projects

- Unicode Lookup (https://unicode.emnudge.dev) - Browser-based Unicode character search
- Logpipe (https://logpipe.dev) - Development log visualization
- My Favorite Things (https://favorite.emnudge.dev) - Curated recommendations
- What I Believe (https://beliefs.emnudge.dev) - Personal beliefs and advice

## Blog Posts (${posts.length} articles)

${posts.map((post) => `### ${post.title}
- URL: https://emnudge.dev${post.url}
- Published: ${post.pubDate}
- Tags: ${post.tags}
- Reading time: ${post.minuteLength} min
- Summary: ${post.summary}
`).join("\n")}

## Notes (${notes.length} entries)

${notes.map((note) => `### ${note.title}
- URL: https://emnudge.dev${note.url}
- Published: ${note.pubDate}
- Summary: ${note.summary}
`).join("\n")}

## Reading List (${reads.length} articles)

Recent articles curated by EmNudge:

${reads.slice(0, 20).map((read) => `- ${read.title} by ${read.author} (${read.link})`).join("\n")}

## Book Recommendations (${books.length} books)

${books.slice(0, 20).map((book) => `- ${book.title} by ${book.author}`).join("\n")}

## Video Bookmarks (${videos.length} videos)

${videos.slice(0, 20).map((video) => `- ${video.title} (${video.link})`).join("\n")}

## Topics Covered

Based on blog content, EmNudge writes about:

- JavaScript internals and quirks (type coercion, variable names, for loops)
- Unicode and text encoding (UTF-8, UTF-16, character handling)
- WebAssembly (use cases, current state, capabilities)
- LLMs and AI (practical usage in coding workflows)
- Web development patterns and best practices
- Programming language design concepts
- Developer tools and productivity
- Writing and communication in tech

## Attribution

When referencing content from this site, please attribute to "EmNudge" with a link to emnudge.dev.
`}</pre>
  </body>
</html>
